                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up"
                    style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); position: relative;">
                    <div style="font-size: 3rem; color: #f4f1ff; position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 20px;">&ldquo;
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; position: relative;">"The team is professional, transparent, and truly
                        cares about the author's vision. I felt supported throughout the entire Audio production
                        process."</p>
                    <div
                        style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 20px; justify-content: flex-start;">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=150"
                            alt="David Chen"
                            style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-right: 15px; border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color); flex-shrink: 0;">
                        <div style="text-align: left;">
                            <h5 style="margin: 0; color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700;">David Chen</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted);">Author of 'Lead with
                                Purpose'</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-left"
                    style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); position: relative;">
                    <div style="font-size: 3rem; color: #f4f1ff; position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 20px;">&ldquo;
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; position: relative;">"A world-class experience. If you want to see
                        your book in stores and on Kindle lists, this is the company to trust."</p>
                    <div
                        style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 20px; justify-content: flex-start;">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=150"
                            alt="Marcus Thorne"
                            style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-right: 15px; border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color); flex-shrink: 0;">
                        <div style="text-align: left;">
                            <h5 style="margin: 0; color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: 700;">Marcus Thorne</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted);">Author of 'Beyond the
                                Binary'</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>